type: software
title: "Coordination Experiment Harness"
abstract: >
  Experimental harness for "Coordination as an Architectural Layer for
  LLM-Based Multi-Agent Systems". Implements five pre-registered
  coordination configurations evaluated on prediction markets under the
  information-fixing principle.
